OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud will soon thin and
OL,6,Fbreak up to give a mostly fine day
OL,7,Fwith bright or sunny spells for many.
OL,8,FFeeling very warm and muggy. Light
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy in the west, clear
OL,12,Fskies develop across the rest of the
OL,13,Fregion during night with light winds.
OL,14,FWarm temperatures and muggy overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FSunny in the east at first
OL,17,Fbefore cloud and rain spreads
OL,18,Feastwards across all parts the
OL,19,Fevening. Feeling warmer than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
